      • ASE.Weight

        public ASE.Weight(java.lang.String address,
          int port,
          int terminal)
           throws java.lang.Exception
        When this class gets initialized it opens a connection and starts a background thread that sends commands to the weight or simulator class.
        Parameters:
        address - This parameter specifies the address or hostname of the weight.
        port - This parameter specifies the port number to be used.
        terminal - This parameter specifies the terminal number the weight has.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Throw an exception when the connection cannot be established.
